<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>tài yáng xià shān le 迦南1098</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 tài yáng xià shān le, wǎn fēng chuī guò lái. tiān fù zài zhào huàn, hái zi kuài huí jiā.
 yáo yuǎn de tiān biān, yǒu yī zhǐ xiǎo yáng, yé sū zhǎo dào tā, bào zài zhǔ xiōng huái.
 mò rì lái dào le, de shàng yǒu dà zāi. shén de ér nǚ men, xīn zhōng zuì míng bái.
 zūn xíng shén de huà, shí shí yào huǐ gǎi. shuǐ liú qiān nián huí dà hǎi, yé sū yī dìng yào huí lái.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1098</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>